tasks.details:
Create .claude/examples/multi-model-config.json:

```json
{
  "description": "Multi-model API configuration example",
  "note": "Add these to your .env file - never commit actual keys",
  "required_env_vars": {
    "GOOGLE_AI_KEY": {
      "description": "Google AI Studio API key for Gemini",
      "source": "https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey",
      "subscription": "$20/month Google AI plan or free tier"
    },
    "OPENAI_API_KEY": {
      "description": "OpenAI API key for Codex/GPT",
      "source": "https://platform.openai.com/api-keys",
      "subscription": "$20/month ChatGPT Plus or API credits"
    }
  },
  "example_env": [
    "# .env (DO NOT COMMIT)",
    "GOOGLE_AI_KEY=your_google_key_here",
    "OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_key_here"
  ],
  "verification": {
    "gemini": "curl -H 'Authorization: Bearer $GOOGLE_AI_KEY' https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1/models",
    "openai": "curl -H 'Authorization: Bearer $OPENAI_API_KEY' https://api.openai.com/v1/models"
  }
}
```

Also update protect-sensitive-files.sh to include these keys if not already.
